### Manual Verification
1. Run `npm run dev` — starts the Next.js integrated development server
2. Verify 3D globe renders with terrain and satellite imagery (ensuring SSR is properly disabled for the globe component)
3. Toggle layers via layer panel
4. Drag timeline to filter events
5. Test camera preset fly-tos
6. Resize browser — panels collapse gracefully

> [!TIP]
> First run requires `VITE_CESIUM_TOKEN` in `.env` (free from [cesium.com/ion](https://cesium.com/ion)). App shows a warning if missing but still renders a basic globe.
